{"tid":2422783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潘兆初宣讀裁決時口罩「戴一個、爛一個」 司法機構指有關口罩在中國製造","createTime":"2021-02-25T12:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:55:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"954626e2ad40974ba610408c0c89601c2d4b9db0","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O9lFqP1Ixay4nOJ_-OYBAGupFiw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DNJEA52OS5FXDEKKELCXQ5IQAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO9lFqP1Ixay4nOJ_-OYBAGupFiw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDNJEA52OS5FXDEKKELCXQ5IQAM.jpg&h=4614f06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民去年元旦日發起遊行，其間有便衣警遇襲，兩名青年經審訊後襲警罪成，原本判監3個月，惟律政司認為刑期過輕，向上訴庭提出刑期覆核。上訴庭亦接納律政司說法，改判兩人入獄10個月。庭上今出現小插曲，原本全程戴口罩的高院首席法官潘兆初，宣讀裁決時一度忘記戴口罩，詎料之後戴一個、爛一個，屢試不爽。最終潘官向身旁的上訴庭法官彭偉昌說了句「放棄」後，在沒戴口罩的情況下宣讀判決。司法機構回覆查詢指，有關口罩並非懲教署出品，而是在中國製造。<br />\n<br />\n是次上訴由高院首席法官潘兆初、上訴庭法官彭偉昌以及原訟庭法官潘敏琦審理。原本全程戴口罩的潘兆初法官，在聽完與訟雙方陳詞後，在內庭與另外兩名法官考慮及商討，隨後返回法庭打算宣讀判決。惟他未待坐下，便突然察覺自己忘記戴口罩，遂急忙指示書記進入內庭代他取口罩，其間全庭人士均默默等候。<br />\n<br />\n稍後，書記將口罩交給潘兆初法官，惟他甫戴上，便發現口罩右邊索帶斷掉了。旁聽人士見狀，不禁笑了出聲。潘官只好再向書記示意「條帶斷咗」。書記返回內庭再取，今次更拿出整整一盒口罩來。潘官親自挑選了一個口罩戴上，詎料索帶又斷。潘官堅持不懈，再戴另一個，卻仍是一戴便斷。此時旁聽席再次傳出笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n最終潘官搖搖頭，輕聲對身旁的法官彭偉昌說：「放棄。」並在無戴口罩下宣讀判決。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構回覆查詢指，有關口罩由政府物流服務署分發給司法機構，在中國製造，並非懲教署出品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/WUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FWUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=a47286e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FWUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU%2F&h=31e24e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/WUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU/</a>"},{"pid":"31e3329a7a29cd6e29948ffc9dfd91d911bdef72","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a33f7c1a907b885554b08eee7869f34715491a","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba22cb3a4709b62fac0410b833d777e2c0cc1502","tid":2422783,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:37:28.000Z","msg":"無CSI用咁陰功豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e431c2474d345ad2f4b35f2b9dc169dadf803a14","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba22cb3a4709b62fac0410b833d777e2c0cc1502","tid":2422783,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:37:28.000Z","msg":"無CSI用咁陰功豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=