rc=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n必遭天譴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21eec1c3576a66252b3c1bca2e4bba4399baad4","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbbbd3b379b72dbf3be8a23cadf289de32abcab","tid":2422783,"uid":263648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"954626e2ad40974ba610408c0c89601c2d4b9db0","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O9lFqP1Ixay4nOJ_-OYBAGupFiw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DNJEA52OS5FXDEKKELCXQ5IQAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO9lFqP1Ixay4nOJ_-OYBAGupFiw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDNJEA52OS5FXDEKKELCXQ5IQAM.jpg&h=4614f06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民去年元旦日發起遊行，其間有便衣警遇襲，兩名青年經審訊後襲警罪成，原本判監3個月，惟律政司認為刑期過輕，向上訴庭提出刑期覆核。上訴庭亦接納律政司說法，改判兩人入獄10個月。庭上今出現小插曲，原本全程戴口罩的高院首席法官潘兆初，宣讀裁決時一度忘記戴口罩，詎料之後戴一個、爛一個，屢試不爽。最終潘官向身旁的上訴庭法官彭偉昌說了句「放棄」後，在沒戴口罩的情況下宣讀判決。司法機構回覆查詢指，有關口罩並非懲教署出品，而是在中國製造。<br />\n<br />\n是次上訴由高院首席法官潘兆初、上訴庭法官彭偉昌以及原訟庭法官潘敏琦審理。原本全程戴口罩的潘兆初法官，在聽完與訟雙方陳詞後，在內庭與另外兩名法官考慮及商討，隨後返回法庭打算宣讀判決。惟他未待坐下，便突然察覺自己忘記戴口罩，遂急忙指示書記進入內庭代他取口罩，其間全庭人士均默默等候。<br />\n<br />\n稍後，書記將口罩交給潘兆初法官，惟他甫戴上，便發現口罩右邊索帶斷掉了。旁聽人士見狀，不禁笑了出聲。潘官只好再向書記示意「條帶斷咗」。書記返回內庭再取，今次更拿出整整一盒口罩來。潘官親自挑選了一個口罩戴上，詎料索帶又斷。潘官堅持不懈，再戴另一個，卻仍是一戴便斷。此時旁聽席再次傳出笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n最終潘官搖搖頭，輕聲對身旁的法官彭偉昌說：「放棄。」並在無戴口罩下宣讀判決。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構回覆查詢指，有關口罩由政府物流服務署分發給司法機構，在中國製造，並非懲教署出品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/WUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FWUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=a47286e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FWUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU%2F&h=31e24e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/WUIHV7UHXFFEXOTGSFJ2CYSSWU/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"天都知道，邊個行不公義。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n必遭天譴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbac9cf40868ff532d8f41511e722600ef807587","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a07c5a213ea89dd09eece65a0621f4aa9b66129","tid":2422783,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0880d3b66acaf163ddf57a1b7295fd6a48192fb7","tid":2422783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37d917b5595407fc4f905c4bc501a5a47536f993","tid":2422783,"uid":42250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"平民唔戴就告<br />\n法官唔戴就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk